 Nhược Kim</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/Ngh%E1%BB%87-T%C4%A9nh-v%C4%83n-th%C3%A2n-%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu-Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-li%C3%AAn/poem-ZUEg1F9gYr2ZCKNuoPgxpA">Nghệ Tĩnh văn thân điếu Phan Đình Phùng đối liên - 乂靜文紳弔潘廷逢對聯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-D%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-H%E1%BA%A1o/S%C6%A1n-pha-d%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BA%A1c-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95/poem-v3b20eOzKpoxOaduzOQBNg">Sơn pha dương - Lạc Dương hoài cổ - 山坡羊－洛陽懷古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-D%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-H%E1%BA%A1o/author-1mWeET7gheMnCvlHowk0Fg">Trương Dưỡng Hạo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%A9-t%C3%B9ng/poem-gGXMjqTTUrdwriPEB0cMQw">Tứ tùng - 四松</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-Chi%E1%BA%BFm-Mai/%E1%BB%A8c-t%C3%ADch/poem-xjVNXSKgaiD21dYg3VRC6g">Ức tích - 憶昔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-Chi%E1%BA%BFm-Mai/author-KcW-7-TuArU6v2a0Re1ZdQ">Lâm Chiếm Mai</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
